    <span class="err">]}</span>
    <span class="na">scrollTo=</span><span class="s2">"body"</span>
<span class="p">/&gt;</span>
</code></pre><h3 id='using-one-view-type'>Using one view type</h3>
<p>If you only want to use the grid view or list view, you need to specify on the <code>hits</code> component, the <code>mod</code> prop to be either <code>sk-hits-list</code> for list components or <code>sk-hits-grid</code> for grid components.</p>
<pre class="highlight jsx tab-jsx"><code>  <span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="nx">Hits</span> <span class="nx">hitsPerPage</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="p">{</span><span class="mi">10</span><span class="p">}</span> <span class="nx">mod</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">"sk-hits-list"</span> <span class="nx">itemComponent</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="p">{</span><span class="nx">ExampleHitsItem</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="sr">/</span><span class="err">&gt;
</span></code></pre>